sentences.english: Slip-on construction with front and rear goring for a secure, comfortable fit.
sentences.chinese: 滑上建设一个安全，舒适合脚的前部和后部戈林。

sentences.english: The cooling water jackets are arranged on the welding torch from the front part to the back part.
sentences.chinese: 在焊炬上从前部到后部均设有冷却水套。

sentences.english: The front of the car sported a flag.
sentences.chinese: 车的前部挂着一面国旗。

sentences.english: Irregular masses of white tumor are seen over the surface of this uterus that has been opened anteriorly .
sentences.chinese: 自前部打开的子宫可见不规则肿物呈白色。

sentences.english: There were no reported casualties but the front of the building had collapsed.
sentences.chinese: 目前暂无人员伤亡报告，但建筑物前部已经倒塌。

sentences.english: The tour guide gave a running commentary from the front of the coach .
sentences.chinese: 导游在旅游车的前部向游客作连续的现场解说。

sentences.english: Bend the arm to bring the weight up to the front of the shoulder.
sentences.chinese: 曲臂，将哑铃提至肩的前部。

sentences.english: Shawn and Walt were around the front of the church looking at the bell tower while I was exploring the back area.
sentences.chinese: 肖恩和沃尔特在教堂前部检查灯塔而我在后面察看。

sentences.english: Forward right wing to body fairing has several loose screws.
sentences.chinese: 右大翼机身整流罩前部有几颗螺钉松动。

sentences.english: Lumbricidae have the clitellum on the anterior part of the body .

sentences.english: The patient was referred to our clinic due to suspected anterior encephalocele.
sentences.chinese: 患者因怀疑前部的脑膨出来我处就诊。

sentences.english: This should put the least-picked numbers at the front of the array.
sentences.chinese: 此操作应当会把最少选择的号码放在数组的前部。

sentences.english: A hook head for ejection is disposed below the front part of the airplane body.
sentences.chinese: 机身前部下方设置有弹射用的钩头。

sentences.english: Kurt motioned for Tom and Lucy to follow him, and they slinked into the room ahead.
sentences.chinese: 库尔特示意汤姆和露西跟着他，他们潜入房间前部。

sentences.english: He sat in the front of the bus to get a good view of the village.
sentences.chinese: 他坐正在汽车前部，为了更好的瞧农村落的风景。

sentences.english: I was sitting at the front of the plane and made eye contact with the flight attendant.
sentences.chinese: 我坐在飞机前部，和空服员对视了一下。
